## Endpoints

Per the AFASA Engine API contract (v2.3.8):

| Method | Path | Workflow |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/afasa/log/tpp` | TPP creation |
| POST | `/afasa/log/ks` | KS creation |
| POST | `/afasa/log/ml` | ML creation |
| POST | `/afasa/log/thf` | THF creation |
| PATCH | `/afasa/log/tpp/{customerId}` | TPP lift |
| PATCH | `/afasa/log/ks/{customerId}` | KS unlock |
| PATCH | `/afasa/log/ml/{customerId}/{transactionId}` | ML unlock |
| PATCH | `/afasa/log/thf/{customerId}/{transactionId}` | THF lift |

Swagger UI available at: `http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html`

