## Re-running jsbb

To refresh the scaffold (e.g., after a `jsbb` upgrade):

```bash
jsbb init
```

`jsbb init` is idempotent — it preserves your hand-written code in the package directories (`api/`, `domain/`, `persistence/`, `eapi/`, `scheduling/`) and only updates scaffold files (`pom.xml`, `application.yml`, configs, Flyway migrations).

